Space Variant Imaging System Toolbox for MATLAB

INSTALLATION

Windows

1. Unzip the SVIS Toolbox ZIP file.

   (Right-click svistoolbox-#.#.#.zip and select "Extract All".)

2. Move the SVIS Toolbox directory to the MATLAB toolbox directory.

   (Drag and drop svistoolbox-#.#.# to
	"C:\Documents and Settings\<username>\My Documents\MATLAB".)

3. Update your MATLAB path to include the SVIS Toolbox directory.

   (In MATLAB, File|Set Path|Add Folder|
    <select C:\...\MATLAB\svistoolbox-#.#.#>|OK|Save)

Linux

1. Extract the SVIS Toolbox archive files.

   ($ tar xzvf svistoolbox-#.#.#.tgz -C ~/.matlab)

2. Update your MATLAB path to include the new toolbox directory.

   (In MATLAB, File|Set Path|Add Folder|
    <select ~/.matlab/svistoolbox-#.#.#>|OK|Save)

